{"tid":1742069,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"乘客平均多花6分鐘 造成經濟損失高達28.65億元","createTime":"2019-11-20T15:19:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T01:10:15.000Z","uid":241000,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4b657f2ee9b6823ba156ef53932f72c9a94d6a95","tid":1742069,"uid":241000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T15:19:11.000Z","msg":"從運輸署的《交通運輸資料月報》，九巴於2014年的乘客人次是9.552億，若每位乘客平均多花6分鐘在車程上，即是乘客在浪費時間的總數是9552萬小時，如果以2014年的最低工資30元計算，這種時間的浪費造成的經濟損失便高達28.65億元，佔2014年的GDP0.12%。然而，筆者要指出這經濟損失未有考慮其他公共交通工具例如城巴、新巴、公共小巴、居民巴士、港鐵巴士、的士等乘客所面對同樣的時間浪費問題。筆者認為一旦納入其他公共交通乘客的時間損失，交通擠塞為香港造成的直接經濟損失絕對不是一個小的數字。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20150828/19273005\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20150828%2F19273005&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzopBSCas1SUWCM4mOsPk5ns%3D&h=615db334\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20150828%2F19273005&h=73b010d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20150828/19273005</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 各位早d瞓"},{"pid":"42096f80292f69163c1bf3836c84a21d936bb78b","tid":1742069,"uid":331459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T15:19:44.000Z","msg":"手足借位，唔好意思<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港公投  要人！ The world is WATCHING</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1742041\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1742041</a></span>"},{"pid":"b63a7f8d88d0791d0a3b6fced2778dd4d9609296","tid":1742069,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T15:24:42.000Z","msg":"戰役過後，痛定思痛，認清現實，重新出發(抗爭五部曲-前言)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg